salesperson every single time?

00:03:24.047 --> 00:03:25.630
The second was, how
could I train them

00:03:25.630 --> 00:03:27.480
in a very predictable way?

00:03:27.480 --> 00:03:29.150
The third was, how
could I provide them

00:03:29.150 --> 00:03:31.690
with the same quality
and quantity of leads

00:03:31.690 --> 00:03:32.980
every single month?

00:03:32.980 --> 00:03:34.480
And the fourth was,
how could I hold

00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:36.820
them accountable
to the same sales

00:03:36.820 --> 00:03:38.680
process against those leads?

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:41.780
And I figured if I could
achieve those four tactics,

00:03:41.780 --> 00:03:44.410
I'd have a high degree of
likelihood of succeeding

00:03:44.410 --> 00:03:45.730
against my mission.

00:03:45.730 --> 00:03:48.600
